name: 火箭狗 (Rocket Dog)
description: 火箭狗（Rocket Dog）is a high-energy, community driven meme project powered by belief, discipline, and a long-term vision. Inspired by the mindset often shared by CZ (Changpeng Zhao): focus on building, ignore short-term noise, and let fundamentals win. Rocket Dog represents patience, resilience, strong community culture, and consistent forward momentum built for the long run. 火箭狗（Rocket Dog）是一个高能量、由社区驱动的迷因项目，建立在信念、自律和长期愿景之上。灵感来自 CZ（赵长鹏）常提倡的理念：专注建设，忽略短期噪音，让基本面取胜。火箭狗象征耐心、韧性、强大的社区文化以及持续向前的长期动力。
